                <fr:title text="Quotients and surjections">Quotients and <fr:link href="jms-00M8.xml" title="Surjection" addr="jms-00M8" type="local">surjections</fr:link></fr:title>
                <fr:taxon>Example</fr:taxon>
              </fr:frontmatter>
              <fr:mainmatter><fr:p>Let <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[E]]></fr:tex> be an <fr:link href="jms-00L4.xml" title="Equivalence relation" addr="jms-00L4" type="local">equivalence relation</fr:link> on a set <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[A]]></fr:tex>, and let <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[q\colon  A\to  A/E]]></fr:tex> be the <fr:em>quotient function</fr:em> that sends <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[a\in  A]]></fr:tex> to its equivalence class <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[{\mathopen {}\left  [a\right  ]\mathclose {}}_{E}]]></fr:tex>. Then <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[q\colon  A\to  A/E]]></fr:tex> is <fr:link href="jms-00M8.xml" title="Surjection" addr="jms-00M8" type="local">surjective</fr:link>.</fr:p>
 
   
   <fr:tree show-metadata="false" toc="false"><fr:frontmatter><fr:authors><fr:author><fr:link href="jonmsterling.xml" title="Jon Sterling" addr="jonmsterling" type="local">Jon Sterling</fr:link></fr:author></fr:authors><fr:date><fr:year>2024</fr:year><fr:month>1</fr:month><fr:day>29</fr:day></fr:date><fr:anchor>6863</fr:anchor><fr:addr type="machine">unstable/6046</fr:addr><fr:route>unstable-6046.xml</fr:route><fr:title text="" /><fr:taxon>Proof</fr:taxon></fr:frontmatter><fr:mainmatter>
 <fr:p>We must show that for every equivalence class <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[u\in  A/E]]></fr:tex> there exists an element <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[a\in  A]]></fr:tex> such that <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[q{\mathopen {}\left (a\right )\mathclose {}}=u]]></fr:tex>. By definition <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[u={\mathopen {}\left  [a\right  ]\mathclose {}}_{E}=q{\mathopen {}\left (a\right )\mathclose {}}]]></fr:tex> for some <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[a\in  A]]></fr:tex>.</fr:p>
</fr:mainmatter></fr:tree>
 
</fr:mainmatter>
